articles.title: French prosecutors seek a 2-year prison sentence and ineligibility period against Marine Le Pen - The Associated Press
articles.description: Paris prosecutors have requested a 2-year prison sentence against France's far-right leader Marine Le Pen and an additional 5-year period of ineligibility to run for office. The request came at a high-profile trial over the suspected embezzlement of European …
